<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 6 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">Scrabble is one of the best educational games you can put in front of a child. It builds vocabulary, reinforces spelling, develops strategic thinking, and teaches basic maths — all disguised as family fun. Here is how to introduce Scrabble to kids aged 6 and up in a way that keeps them engaged and coming back for more.</p>

